text:
Pandey Janni

Waise toh bolne ke liye kaafi chize hai but tmse acha kisko pta hoga ki mereko mimic krr ke batane me kitna maza aata hai. 
Although hmlog ka dosti class 10th se chalu hua tha, but mereko pehli baar yaad hai jab hmlog mile the, FIITJEE me 2nd phase class 9th ke exam me shayd(uss samay tm kaafi patle bhi the). Uske baad toh rest is history. Har exam top krna, har teacher ka favorite hona. Phir toh Allah ka aisa khair hua ki  Same IIT, Same Hall, Bagal wala hostel room. Although hmlog ka future at present diverging hai, but mereko lagta hai phir saath me bakchodi aur dusro ko bully krne me jayda din ni hai.

Tab tak ke liye Khuda Hafiz Pandey Janni.
author: Kumar  Shivam
